<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Wallet ₹100000</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7a0000, #b30000);
    color: white;
}

/* Header */
.header {
    background: #a00000;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Balance Section */
.balance-box {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #ff3c3c, #7a0000);
}

.balance-box h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: normal;
}

.balance {
    font-size: 50px;
    color: gold;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

/* Tips */
.section {
    padding: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #ddd;
}

.section h4 {
    color: white;
}

/* Buttons */
.buttons {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
}

.btn {
    width: 40%;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.withdraw {
    background: #990000;
    color: white;
}

.deposit {
    background: linear-gradient(#ffd700, #ffb300);
    color: black;
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">Wallet</div>

<div class="balance-box">
    <h3>My Balance</h3>
    <div class="balance">₹100000</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h4>Deposit tips:</h4>
    <p>1. Each deposit will be credited within 1-5 minutes.</p>
    <p>2. You can contact customer service anytime.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h4>Withdraw tips:</h4>
    <p>Withdrawal usually arrives within 2 hours (max 24 hours).</p>
</div>

<div class="buttons">
    <button class="btn withdraw">Withdraw</button>
    <button class="btn deposit">Deposit</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
